                    AI Tutor
                    <span className="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                        Beta
